task.summary: Massive cleanup in all framework files. Better compliance with Python standards and general bugfixes found via static analysis. Phase 1 of general cleanup before 0.3 release.
General bugfixes, updated setup.py to include new test modules, which should fix testsuite when installed via pip/setup.
More cleanup, fixing PEP8 violations and formatting tests.
Bugfixes in the inmemory adapter, including an issue preventing inequality filters from functioning properly.
Working Graph models and implementation for InMemoryAdapter, along with tests to verify working interfaces. Progress on FLY-26, FLY-27, and FLY-24. Substantial progress on FLY-4 and FLY-1.
Bugfixes for 'CallbackProxy' bugs found in the course of FLY-27, along with tests and docstrings.
Bugfixes for 'BidirectionalEnum' bugs found in the course of FLY-1 and FCM-69, along with tests and docstrings.
Final bug concerning reverse-enum-resolution fixed in 'BidirectionalEnum'.
Bugfixes in ProtoRPC model/key adapters, found in the course of work on FLY-1.
Beginnings of indexer overrides for FLY-25. Instrumenting abstract and reference adapter implementations.
